    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting, but is that really a \"consensus\"? i feel like i hear a lot of economists saying it's way more complicated than just \"incentives.\" like, what about things like automation or just the aging population? wouldn't those be bigger factors than just the welfare programs?",
